  "texts": [
    "Therefore, verification of the new instructions is a crucial step for this type of augmentation.",
    "We employ two methods for instruction-following augmentation: 1) Task Instruction Rephrasing.",
    "We rephrase the task instructions using powerful LLMs to accommodate various input styles from users.",
    "To ensure the rephrased instructions still align with the original version, we verify them by prompting the LLMs with the rephrased instructions and check if the LLMs can still follow them and generate correct function calls.",
    "2) Format Instruction-Following."
  ],
